00:02:48.830 --> 00:02:49.470
Good to hear.

00:02:49.470 --> 00:02:51.460
[SPEAKING CHINESE]

00:02:56.790 --> 00:02:58.224
I've just told
them that if anyone

00:02:58.224 --> 00:03:00.640
tries to leave this talk early,
then they'll hold the door

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:03.056
and make sure you stay for the
